9️⃣ Clean-up Commands
Stop all containers
docker stop $(docker ps -aq)

Remove all containers
docker rm $(docker ps -aq)

Remove all images
docker rmi $(docker images -q)

Remove everything (DANGER)
docker system prune -a


🔟 Tagging Images
